Class BoaRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.repository.boa.BoaRepository

  • public class BoaRepository
extends java.lang.Object
    A repository for BOA components. A BOA component repository is special because it contains 4 lists instead of 1 list of rep items. immutable.
